@platform android 0.8 @platform blackberry 3.1.2 @platform iphone 0.8 @platform ipad 0.8 @platform mobileweb 1.8 @pseudo @editurl https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/edit/master/apidoc/Modules/Modules.yml

Optional Titanium modules.

@description

Modules in this section are optional modules that may be packaged with the Titanium SDK. These modules are not part of the Titanium namespace, and must be added to the tiapp.xml file and imported using require.

Each of the modules in this section is either packaged with the Titanium SDK or available for free through the Appcelerator Marketplace.
